\frac{1}{1-z^n}=1+z^n+z^{2n}+\cdots\Longrightarrow \frac{z^n}{1-z^n}=z^n+z^{2n}+z^{3n}+\cdots
\frac{z^n}{1-z^n}=\sum_{\{m\in\mathbb{N}_0:n|m\}}z^m
\sum_{n=1}^{+\infty}\frac{z^n}{1-z^n}=\sum_{m=1}^{+\infty} d(m)\,z^m.
